&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Reinstitution of ranger only bows&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Effects of gear on archery&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Addition of different archery effects&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;No Drop Arrows on loot tables&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;5.&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Improved heals&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffff00&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;-&lt;/STRONG&gt; Pending with reinvisioning -&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;This&amp;nbsp;is being considered as part #1 of the class Re-Envision process.&amp;nbsp; Some of these changes have made their way to Test Server.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Suggestions on focus&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;UL&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Rangers understand they are not primary healers&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Quick casting&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Decent total hp heal totals&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Decent mana ratios&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Balanced well with Parent class and other hybrids&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;6.&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Improved Disciplines&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;Currently being discussed&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;UL&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;Addition of melee disciplins&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Reduction of current discipline timers (60+ minutes)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;7.&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Improve Auspice of the Hunter /&amp;nbsp;Increase raid&amp;nbsp;desirability&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;Changes to this AA have been pushed to Test Server.&amp;nbsp; These changes have not been passed by QA so they may not be final.&amp;nbsp; The general idea however is "The boost Auspice gives is being doubled and an increase to heal crit rates has been added."&lt;FONT face="Century Gothic"&gt;&lt;FONT color=#000000&gt;&lt;FONT size=2&gt;&lt;B normal? **SMURF**?mso-bidi-font-weight:&gt;&lt;xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" &gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Suggestions for focus&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;UL&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Please parse the totals of this MGB'd on a raid&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Parse totals when used in a group&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Add extra benefit fo the AoH caster&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Remove the casting time completely&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;8.&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Buff Problems&lt;/STRONG&gt; -&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Currently being&amp;nbsp;discussed, this will most likely be considered as part of the class Re-Envision process.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Suggestions for areas of improvement&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;UL&gt;&#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Viability of high levels of attack, which is the only unique style of buff rangers get&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Consideration of our&amp;nbsp;Ward of the&amp;nbsp;Hunter&amp;nbsp;buff line&amp;nbsp;being ALL targeted buffs&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Inclusion of other buffs in Ward of the Hunter line (Briarcoat line, Mask of the Stalker, etc)&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Desirability of Spirit of the Hunter vs Brells or Spritual Vitality lines&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Caster Desirable buff&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Indoor wolf form should be at least as fast as runspeed 5...&lt;/SPAN&gt; &#xD;
&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Upgrade Onyx Skin to be more of a druid replacement buff, more in line with what other hybrids have&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;9.&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Improve Ranger&amp;nbsp;Detrimental Spells (DDs, Snares, Roots)&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffff00&gt;- Pending with reinvisioning -&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;This&amp;nbsp;is being considered as part #1 of the class Re-Envision process.&amp;nbsp; Some of these changes have made their way to Test Server.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
